thread.title: Lisa

author: Lisa
title: Lisa
text: Excellent products...every year I treat myself to a couple of ornaments to add to my collection. They have great choices with new colors added every year. Great quality for the price point! I also appreciate that my order is always shipped in a timely manner and is wrapped well as to protect during the trip! So many other things I would love to order...one day when I have a little extra $$ I'm going to splurge!
